      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, a \"new path\" requires someone to walk it. and there's nobody left here. the version of me that was worth something, the one that had a future... that person is gone. it's like there's just this empty, broken thing standing here instead. it feels so much more logical to just let it be over than to try and pretend i'm still \"me\".",
