    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't think \"healing\" is even an option when the core of who i was is just destroyed. it feels like a lie, trying to fix something that's fundamentally hollow now. honestly... if that person is already dead, then what's the point of the rest of this? it's just dragging out the inevitable, isn't it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
